'''賀穆士治.律敦治'''，（'''Hormusjee Ruttonjee'''，{{bd|1860年|6月22日|1944年|12月20日}}<ref>[http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&GRid=62048013 Hormusjee Ruttonjee] {{Wayback|url=http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&GRid=62048013 |date=20150402144343 }} Find a Grave</ref>），是一位在香港的[[巴斯人|巴斯人]]，在[[孟買|孟買]]出生。H.律敦治於1884年抵港<ref>[https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=OzIOBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA147&lpg=PA147&dq=Hormusjee+Ruttonjee&source=bl&ots=DaWMnDsrQ2&sig=TNWm7G1f0RNgwReYu0xyqxQD0EI&hl=en&sa=X&ei=o50NVcurJpDo8AWiroGgCQ&ved=0CDUQ6AEwBDgy#v=onepage&q=Hormusjee%20Ruttonjee&f=false Society] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=OzIOBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA147&lpg=PA147&dq=Hormusjee+Ruttonjee&source=bl&ots=DaWMnDsrQ2&sig=TNWm7G1f0RNgwReYu0xyqxQD0EI&hl=en&sa=X&ei=o50NVcurJpDo8AWiroGgCQ&ved=0CDUQ6AEwBDgy#v=onepage&q=Hormusjee%20Ruttonjee&f=false |date=20150402095659 }} David Faure, Hong Kong University Press</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.macaudata.com/macaubook/book128/html/07701.htm |title=瑣羅亞斯德教(Zoroastrianism) |accessdate=2015-03-21 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402123756/http://www.macaudata.com/macaubook/book128/html/07701.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=PUfHAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA158&lpg=PA158&dq=Hormusjee+Ruttonjee&source=bl&ots=4Vicmn8_je&sig=vhD7wRbqBJ3QXqsO1SpHvNSnvDQ&hl=en&sa=X&ei=s5wNVcTTBoS78gX26oHQCw&ved=0CDAQ6AEwBDgK#v=onepage&q=Hormusjee%20Ruttonjee&f=false Foreign Communities in Hong Kong, 1840s-1950s] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=PUfHAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA158&lpg=PA158&dq=Hormusjee+Ruttonjee&source=bl&ots=4Vicmn8_je&sig=vhD7wRbqBJ3QXqsO1SpHvNSnvDQ&hl=en&sa=X&ei=s5wNVcTTBoS78gX26oHQCw&ved=0CDAQ6AEwBDgK#v=onepage&q=Hormusjee%20Ruttonjee&f=false |date=20150402130126 }} Cindy Yik-yi Chu, Palgrave Macmillan</ref>，在香港及廣州的洋行工作，1887年成立律敦治洋行（H. Ruttonjee & Son）。1913年將公司交給兒子[[J.H.律敦治|J.H.律敦治]]打理，公司發展為知名家族企業<ref>[https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=krIQBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA187&lpg=PA187&dq=H.%E5%BE%8B%E6%95%A6%E6%B2%BB&source=bl&ots=-xsBiSoSD9&sig=ml1eUyGYlhYsQAlx2ZLfnZx8Bjo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=IZoNVfqCDZXn8AX78YGIBg&ved=0CEoQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=H.%E5%BE%8B%E6%95%A6%E6%B2%BB&f=false 非我族裔：戰前香港的外籍族群] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=krIQBgAAQBAJ&pg=PA187&lpg=PA187&dq=H.%E5%BE%8B%E6%95%A6%E6%B2%BB&source=bl&ots=-xsBiSoSD9&sig=ml1eUyGYlhYsQAlx2ZLfnZx8Bjo&hl=en&sa=X&ei=IZoNVfqCDZXn8AX78YGIBg&ved=0CEoQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=H.%E5%BE%8B%E6%95%A6%E6%B2%BB&f=false |date=20150402123209 }}丁新豹, 三聯書店(香港)有限公司 2014</ref>。1898年英國租借新界後，律敦治父子開始在深井購入大量土地，在1930年代初期在[[深井|深井]]興建香港首座釀酒廠[[香港生力啤酒廠|香港啤酒廠有限公司]]（'''Hong Kong Brewery'''），持有大量深井物業<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cache.org.hk/blog/waller_and_sham_tseng/ |title=窩拿與深井 – 村民回憶中的生力啤廠長 （溫詩） |accessdate=2015-03-27 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402163304/http://cache.org.hk/blog/waller_and_sham_tseng/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ol.mingpao.com/cfm/style5.cfm?File=20140427%2Fsta13%2Fuaf1.txt |title=街知巷聞﹕深井發迹 關生力啤事 |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2020-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612114128/https://ol.mingpao.com/cfm/style5.cfm?File=20140427%2Fsta13%2Fuaf1.txt |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20071110/10402891 |title=蘋果資訊：開業逾半世紀　深井燒鵝始祖 |accessdate=2015-03-27 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402142158/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20071110/10402891 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20121124/18078297 |title=陳記燒鵝後人 深井「山寨王」 |accessdate=2015-03-27 |archive-date=2016-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723090946/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20121124/18078297 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且興建白樓作為別墅。後來白樓被[[港英政府|香港政府]]購買作為[[香港公務員|香港公務員]][[宿舍|宿舍]]，1995年被有關[[香港政府部門|香港政府部門]]闢作展覽中心，介紹《香港機場核心計劃》，於1996年年初開放。[[古物諮詢委員會|古物諮詢委員會]]於2010年1月22日將白樓確認評為[[三級歷史建築|三級歷史建築]]<ref>「[http://www.lcsd.gov.hk/ce/Museum/Monument/form/AAB-SM-chi.pdf 1444幢歷史建築物名單和評估結果] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lcsd.gov.hk/ce/Museum/Monument/form/AAB-SM-chi.pdf |date=20111215155849 }}」古物古蹟辦事處</ref>。兒子J.H.律敦治在1943年<ref>[http://sunzi1.lib.hku.hk/newspaper/view/09_01.01/93242.pdf Prominent philanthropist died], South China Morning Post, July 29, 1974</ref>成立了「香港防癆會」（[[香港防癆心臟及胸病協會|香港防癆心臟及胸病協會]]前身）<ref>[http://www.ha.org.hk/org/antitb/tb_ehist.htm History] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ha.org.hk/org/antitb/tb_ehist.htm |date=20150924024542 }}, Hong Kong Tuberculosis, Chest and Heart Diseases Association, Accessed 2007-06/23</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.travelqna.org/travel/archives/24504 |title=巴斯墳場 |accessdate=2015-03-21 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402120833/http://www.travelqna.org/travel/archives/24504 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。孫兒為前[[香港立法局議員|香港立法局議員]][[鄧律敦治|鄧律敦治]]。

